---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Digital Assets"
  description="Lavelle Pty Ltd develops and operates a growing portfolio of digital assets across professional services, local business information, property, construction and digital products."
>
  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy-300 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Lavelle Pty Ltd</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Digital Assets</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          A growing portfolio of digital assets built around useful content, searchable information, commercial intent and repeatable systems.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Alongside its consulting and PMO resource work, Lavelle Pty Ltd develops and operates a growing portfolio of digital assets. These assets are designed around useful content, searchable information, commercial intent and repeatable systems.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          The portfolio includes assets across professional services, local business information, property and renovation content, construction-related markets and digital products. Each asset is built with a focus on search visibility, practical user value, commercial conversion and long-term scalability.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ASSET CHARACTERISTICS -->
  <section class="section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-xl mb-10">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Approach</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">How the Portfolio Is Built</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {[
          {
            title: 'Search Visibility',
            description:
              'Assets are built with a clear view of search intent. Content structures, taxonomy and technical performance are designed to support organic discovery and long-term ranking.',
          },
          {
            title: 'Practical User Value',
            description:
              'Content serves a genuine user need. Each asset is built around information that is useful, accurate and well-structured for the target audience.',
          },
          {
            title: 'Commercial Conversion',
            description:
              'Assets connect organic traffic to commercial outcomes through clear pathways, commercial intent matching and appropriate conversion structures.',
          },
          {
            title: 'Repeatable Systems',
            description:
              'Content, technical and operational systems are designed to be repeatable and scalable across the portfolio rather than bespoke to individual assets.',
          },
          {
            title: 'Long-Term Scalability',
            description:
              'Each asset is built with a durable structure that can grow over time through additional content, expanded coverage and improved commercial integration.',
          },
          {
            title: 'Technical Performance',
            description:
              'Assets are built on performant, maintainable technical stacks with a focus on page speed, accessibility and crawlability.',
          },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="flex flex-col p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">{item.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Digital Asset Enquiries</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          For enquiries related to the Lavelle Pty Ltd digital asset portfolio, use the contact form and select "Digital Asset Enquiry" as the enquiry type.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-navy-800 hover:bg-navy-900 rounded-md transition-colors"
        >
          Send an Enquiry
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
